Find the perimeter of this shape, which is not drawn to scale. Simplify the perimeter expression as much as possible.

>> [@image(insertGraph($image_1), width=>282, alt=>qq"a six-sided shape whose sides are labeled 3/2 A, 2/3 B, 3/4 C, 2A, 2/3 B, and 8/17 C")@]*  <<

